column5: Good to hear your missing all that nasty stuff Fred.  As for the deposit, I've got a call into Charlene as we speak.  Gonna be an awful long 9 months though
Happy Birthday Lew, and many more.  How many spanks this time
How many spanks this time  I don't have enough fingers & toes to count that high Joey
Happy Birthday Lew! It was nice meeting you and Diane this past summer and thanks again for helping me out !
Thanks Matt and the pleasure was all mine.  Maybe the 4 of us  can get together over the winter for dinner.
A day late and.....well you know.  Belated "best wishes" Lew.
Thanks Chris, much appreciated as always.
Many happy returns Lew. Kelvin nailed it.
Kelvin nailed it.  Thanks spincast and your 100% correct on Kelvin.
Back to the top.  Happy birthday Lew.   May as well make a week of it.
Back to the top.  Happy birthday Lew.   May as well make a week of it.  Thanks Connie, I'm gonna need some more birthday cake if this party continues
Every Birthday is a special one Lew when you're like over 100 and all.  Spank!!!
Your not far off Drew LOL
Happy belated birthday Lew.
Happy belated Birthday Lew, glad you had a great day, and here's to many many more  Maureen
Thanks Phil & Maureen, much appreciated.
Have a great one my friend!
Hope your having a great day my friend. HAPPY B-DAY
Happy birthday Lew,hope you have a good one!!!!!!!!!!!!!!. Seems like you have a lot to celebrate as well.!!
Happy bday Lew!! I hope you have a great day with the ladies in your life!!!
All the very best to you Lew! Remember, birthdays are good, the more you have the longer you live!
Thanks fellas, very nice of you and davey your right, I have more to celebrate now than I ever thought I  would.
Happy Birthday Lew!!
Enjoy your day Lew... and I see you already looked around and saw your present!
Happy Birthday my friend...
Thanks Will and you've got that right Wayne.
Thanks to you too Norm, we were typing at the same time.
Happy birthday my friend.   Hope all is well in your home
Thanks Rich, it couldn't be much better around here.
Happy Birthday Lew, best of health for you and the Mrs.  Enjoy the early snow.
Thanks Bud, things are looking good now.
Hope you had a great day Lew.  Happy birthday!!
happy birthday Lew, another trip around the sun starts, may you have many, many more trips.
happy bday Lew!  smile for cryin out loud!  hope your day was awesome!
Happy birthday Lew! Hope you had a good one!
HAPPY BIRTHDAY my friend you might just have gotten the best Birthday Present Ever    All the Best Lew to you and Diane
Happy Birthday!  I hope you have many more.

HAPPY BIRTHDAY my friend you might just have gotten the best Birthday Present Ever    All the Best Lew to you and Diane  Thanks once again folks, and as Kelvin  said, I received the only thing I wanted.
Happy belated birthday my friend!!!
Thanks Fred, hope your avoiding all the crazy Buffalo snow.

We're thankfully about 30 miles to the south of the snowbelt Lew, and in the case of this event we're quite a ways south. Received notice that it's time for our cabin deposit this week. It's one bill I look forward to every year.
